WEBVTT

00:08:28.061 --> 00:08:30.403
where our instruments sit
and process that light.

00:08:30.831 --> 00:08:32.765
What's new in SDSS-V

00:08:32.789 --> 00:08:36.510
is that we're making the focal plane
entirely robotic.

00:08:37.051 --> 00:08:39.159
That's right: robots.

00:08:39.183 --> 00:08:40.333
(Laughter)

00:08:41.019 --> 00:08:43.125
So I'm going to show them to you,

00:08:43.149 --> 00:08:46.782
but they're fierce and terrifying,

00:08:46.806 --> 00:08:48.826
and I want you all to just take a breath.

00:08:49.450 --> 00:08:51.204
(Exhales) Trigger warning.

00:08:51.722 --> 00:08:55.562
And with no apologies to all
the Blade Runners among you,

00:08:56.516 --> 00:08:57.873
here they are.

00:08:57.897 --> 00:08:59.610
(Laughter)

00:08:59.634 --> 00:09:01.029
I have 1,000 of these,